# NestJS Backend Rules

- Feature modules under `apps/api/src/modules/<feature>/`
- Thin controllers; inject services; use `@RequirePermissions()` from `@varnarc/auth`
- Zod schemas in `@varnarc/validation`; validate with `ZodValidationPipe`
- Inject `REPOS` from `database.module` — use repository methods, not raw Prisma in services
- Return `ok(data)` / `okCursor(page)` from `common/utils/response`
- Log security-relevant events via `SecurityEventsService` when appropriate
- Add Vitest specs in `apps/api/test/` or colocated `*.spec.ts`
- Register module in `app.module.ts`; add Swagger `@ApiTags` on controllers

